---
title: Lemony Garlic-Parmesan Salmon with Veggies and Linguine
description: Tender and flaky salmon is getting the royal treatment for tonight's dinner. Crusted in a toasted panko-Parmesan topping before being roasted, it's then served over luxurious veggie-loaded linguine.
